{"tid":813881,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒人想試下beach hunting / treasure hunting(metal detecting)","createTime":"2018-09-10T21:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T10:39:31.000Z","uid":89939,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58e540cb1f3c0b807aaef920a68dffe1b880317c","tid":813881,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T21:12:00.000Z","msg":"Metal detecting係香港係一種完全沒人聽過既興趣<br />\n<br />\n買部手持金屬探測器去沙灘揾銀仔或者上山搵子彈都得, 當尋寶咁玩 <br />\n<br />\n我可以推薦一啲入門gear, 入門探測器大約二千之內都好多選擇, 想搵人組團一齊去掃沙灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港都有一隊外國人組成既探測隊, 專門上山揾二戰物品<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b-THAvd1ItM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db-THAvd1ItM&d=jwgvwYm1PccCAHRL%2FKo1P%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bc444127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b-THAvd1ItM</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地甚至搵到1947年墜機遺失既墨西哥金幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/magazines/post-magazine/long-reads/article/2067213/hong-kong-history-buffs-return-plane-crash-site\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpost-magazine%2Flong-reads%2Farticle%2F2067213%2Fhong-kong-history-buffs-return-plane-crash-site&d=jwgvwYm1PccCAHRL%2FKo1P%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ec6d7d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/magazines/post-magazine/long-reads/article/2067213/hong-kong-history-buffs-return-plane-crash-site</a><br />\n<br />\n掃淺水灣:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vfFcu91_-o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4vfFcu91_-o&d=jwgvwYm1PccCAHRL%2FKo1P%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=60de1b2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vfFcu91_-o</a><br />\n<br />\n之前沙灘自己一個掃既成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/i64KDk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fi64KDk.jpg&h=1cdc84db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/vWAXTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FvWAXTx.jpg&h=214467b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/fdZPwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FfdZPwx.jpg&h=d3889883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人有興趣既會開telegram group傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e775642fdcbc250fd9cf0a98dbb71814303f63a9","tid":813881,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T21:16:33.000Z","msg":"咁多銀 有冇邊啲係有價值"},{"pid":"00b7a8c32e7d750b7d16021337d10622182a04db","tid":813881,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T22:12:51.000Z","msg":"之前有單新聞好似就係呢隊外國人掃到2個炸彈<br />\n幾得意的興趣"},{"pid":"0c8cf4b91af5b8f3dc191ec93fd9e061d23531ae","tid":813881,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e775642fdcbc250fd9cf0a98dbb71814303f63a9","tid":813881,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T21:16:33.000Z","msg":"咁多銀 有冇邊啲係有價值"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"太生鏽既, 只可以用係汽水機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca60ac69873de2244b8d77e62194c22124691b61","tid":813881,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c8cf4b91af5b8f3dc191ec93fd9e061d23531ae","tid":813881,"uid":89939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e775642fdcbc250fd9cf0a98dbb71814303f63a9","tid":813881,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T21:16:33.000Z","msg":"咁多銀 有冇邊啲係有價值"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"太生鏽既, 只可以用係汽水機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class